{"type":"article","id":13988,"title":"豆瓣图书《改革历程》的故事","uid":749,"topics":[4668],"contents":"豆瓣网上有一本叫《改革历程》的书，该书作者是高尚全。<br>\n由于和赵紫阳的回忆录同名，所以网友们都在这本书下面点评赵紫阳的回忆录。<br>\n豆瓣后来就关闭了该书的评论。<br>\nhttps://book.douban.com/subject/3393295/<br>\n<br>\n我今晚查看旧照片时，无意间发现我几年前留有几张该书的评价截图，故发上来和各葱友分享。<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/19f0b6fdd775d72d3f333.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/19f0b6fdd775d72d3f333.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/19f0b6fdd775d72d3f333.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/63ab117auntrusted fake 2049bbsgra.ph/file/63ab117a2fc043aaaf037.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/63ab117a2fc043aaaf037.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4255a174e6b272aa08b9a.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4255a174e6b272aa08b9a.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4255a174e6b272aa08b9a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/43f0f6afe3fc0710888dc.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/43f0f6afe3fc0710888dc.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/43f0f6afe3fc0710888dc.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<i>(这张图是从微博上找到的）</i><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n知乎上也能找到证据。<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d4b8b07ba00b4098fd71c.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d4b8b07ba00b4098fd71c.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d4b8b07ba00b4098fd71c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-08","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}